{"tid":1185584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港 男警瞞擁12幅地呃學資處罪成 還柙兩周後判刑","createTime":"2019-06-04T10:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:33:39.000Z","uid":53568,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fae0bd39c0127b4dde3b903b417e4c067cf01145","tid":1185584,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015547-香港-男警瞞擁12幅地呃學資處罪成+還柙兩周後判刑+\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1015547-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E7%9E%9E%E6%93%8112%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%B0%E5%91%83%E5%AD%B8%E8%B3%87%E8%99%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%2B%E9%82%84%E6%9F%99%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%2B&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=92e4bdbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1015547-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E7%9E%9E%E6%93%8112%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%B0%E5%91%83%E5%AD%B8%E8%B3%87%E8%99%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%2B%E9%82%84%E6%9F%99%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91%2B&h=afbe762c\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015547-香港-男警瞞擁12幅地呃學資處罪成+還柙兩周後判刑+</a><br />\n<br />\n26歲男警為大埔梧桐寨村原居民，涉嫌於2013及2014年就學期間，申請學生資助時，向學資處隱瞞名下擁有12幅大埔土地，成功騙取19.3萬港元資助。涉案男警被控兩項欺詐罪，今在西九龍裁判法院被裁定罪名成立 ，劉淑嫻暫委裁判官在判刑時指被告的欺騙行為屬有意圖欺騙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b09466dc8c994505e9760bc2902ad4187d2ea3","tid":1185584,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fae0bd39c0127b4dde3b903b417e4c067cf01145","tid":1185584,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015547-香港-男警瞞擁12幅地